{"tid":2390740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Telegram被指促進暴力極端主義　被要求從Google play平台下架","createTime":"2021-02-01T18:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T19:34:31.000Z","uid":320575,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f9d7075b2a3c9b4f6654f7236c12a001b8855a27","tid":2390740,"uid":320575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T18:30:03.000Z","msg":"早前美國國會爆發衝突事件，被指鼓吹煽動暴力行為的右翼社交平台Parler，遭到各大科企封殺。最近，通訊軟件Telegram也成為針對目標之一。最近一名前美國大使指出，Telegram促進暴力極端主義，並向Google提出起訴，要求其程式從Google play下架。<br />\n<br />\n據外媒報道，美國前駐摩洛哥大使Marc Ginsberg，最近在加州法院向提出訴訟，要求Google在Google Play商店中下架Telegram。他指出，Telegram平台充斥納粹主義、煽動暴力行為，以及極端主義等内容，並認為Telegram應與Parler一樣，遭到蘋果（Apple）及Google封殺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對此，Telegram創辦人Pavel Durov表示，在國會大廈發生騷亂事件後，該平台已刪除數百條相關貼文，並表示不容忍任何煽動暴力行為言論。Telegram更表示，程式内採用強大審查機制，以打擊用戶濫用行為及反對恐怖暴力主義。據了解，到目前為止，Google並沒有對此事作出任何回應<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2863804?r=mcsdfbez%3F%3Dr1&amp;fbclid=IwAR07OEHMA4MYRkdtjhfyL4ZaEB6waojW60cPgRW80SE9akaBdaYnP_GYl3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2863804%3Fr%3Dmcsdfbez%253F%253Dr1%26fbclid%3DIwAR07OEHMA4MYRkdtjhfyL4ZaEB6waojW60cPgRW80SE9akaBdaYnP_GYl3A&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=767baa69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2863804?r=mcsdfbez%3F%3Dr1&amp;fbclid=IwAR07OEHMA4MYRkdtjhfyL4ZaEB6waojW60cPgRW80SE9akaBdaYnP_GYl3A</a>"},{"pid":"3c6234a888c6ea7f3cb42a684c2245dd41136555","tid":2390740,"uid":69221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T18:31:18.000Z","msg":"用得Android 就唔洗用Google play 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6e50978bb112d1b77f64b4739a3433c48d26fa","tid":2390740,"uid":103668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T19:16:17.000Z","msg":"屌那星<br />\n有冇大廠出degoogle phone"},{"pid":"0a3068721fe0afa5c6eec500088c35a774fb9150","tid":2390740,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d6e50978bb112d1b77f64b4739a3433c48d26fa","tid":2390740,"uid":103668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T19:16:17.000Z","msg":"屌那星<br />\n有冇大廠出degoogle phone"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T19:34:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://grapheneos.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgrapheneos.org%2F&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=748f4451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://grapheneos.org/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://calyxos.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcalyxos.org%2F&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=84120173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://calyxos.org/</a>"}]}